These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, apricot, light-blue, black
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, game, davidoff, fonseca
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, trance, rock, reggae
 1. the person who likes light-blue is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the fan d&b##3
 3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 4. the davidoff-smoker is the fan d&b##1
 5. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the fan reggae##1
 6. the fan d&b is in an even position##4
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is the fan trance##1
 8. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 9. the fan trance is not the person who likes black##6
10. the fan reggae is on the left or right of the fan d&b##3
11. the fan reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job           | black         | apricot    | light-blue | aquamarine    |
| Nationality   | game        | davidoff | fonseca | alhambra   |
| Sport         | rock | d&b   | reggae  | trance |

