.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-6-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, bellflower, daisy, begonia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, fantasy, scientific, disaster
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, oliveros, alhambra, blend
 1. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
 2. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
 3. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
 4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
 5. the person who growsdaisy is not the person watching scientific movies##6
 6. the blend-smoker is between the game-smoker and the person who growssunflower##2
 7. the person who growsdaisy is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who growsbegonia is between the person who growssunflower and the person watching fantasy movies##2
 9. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
10. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
11. the person who growsdaisy is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Job           | daisy  | begonia    | sunflower | bellflower |
| Music-Genre   | fantasy | crime | disaster     | scientific       |
| Sport         | game   | blend    | oliveros     | alhambra   |

