.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-6-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, bus, quad-bike, tram
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, blend, ritmeester, bluemaster
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, horse, ferret
1. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the tram and the bluemaster-smoker##2
2. the person driving the quad-bike is between the bluemaster-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##2
3. the vegafina-smoker is not the person driving the ship##6
4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the owner of the bird is the person driving the ship##1
7. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the ritmeester-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | tram  | quad-bike  | bus  | ship    |
| Movie-Genre   | vegafina       | blend   | bluemaster | ritmeester |
| Sport         | horse | guinea-pig | ferret   | bird    |

