.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-6-4::.
House: ranch-style, modern, futuristic, gothic-revival
4 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, go, snooker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, fanta, iced-tea
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person playing snooker is not the gothic-revival house##6
 3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 4. the gothic-revival house is between the person playing monopoly and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
 6. the modern house is on the far right##1
 7. the modern house is in an even position##4
 8. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 9. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
10. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
11. the modern house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |       2       |     3      |     4     |
| Food        | ranch-style     | futuristic   | gothic-revival | modern    |
| Job         | go | snooker | backgammon | monopoly |
| Transport   | soy-milk            | iced-tea           | tea        | fanta    |

