 4. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
 5. the person playing backgammon is not the person driving the van##6
 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person playing backgammon##6
 9. the person driving the bike is not the person playing whist##6
10. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
11. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |       3       |     4     |
| Food   | rock-climbing    | writing       | skydiving          | woodworking |
| Job    | bike | boat | roller | van |
| Pet    | bridge       | whist   | backgammon           | domino  |

